OL,6,FHe has since rebuilt his life and his
OL,7,Frelationships and now wants to help
OL,8,Fothers in a similar situation to do
OL,9,Fthe same.
OL,11,FThis January saw the highest monthly
OL,12,Fnumber of calls to GamCare's National
OL,13,FGambling Helpline since it opened -
OL,14,Fwith 4,816 calls and online chats made
OL,15,Facross the month.
OL,17,FLisa Patton from the charity says
OL,18,Fgambling is a "hidden addiction" and
OL,19,Fthe first step in getting help is
OL,20,Fstarting the conversation.
