OL,6,F"People have to find out what support
OL,7,Fis out there and we offer a free
OL,8,Fsupport service for people who are
OL,9,Fexperiencing harm from gambling and
OL,10,Faffected others," she said.
OL,12,F"It's not just the person who is
OL,13,Fgambling, there can be six to twelve
OL,14,Fother people impacted by someone's
OL,15,Fgambling."
